    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Plutobell 处于危险之中</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《RoboGAL：Gaga Delta Lady》中，您将帮助 Rei-Bo 调查坠毁在 Plutobell 上的飞船，飞船上布满了各种陷阱和敌人！跳跃、射击和滑行，克服游戏中的所有障碍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/220c317a7822216c95f229db971e2003.poster.avif?t=1767996601\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/220c317a7822216c95f229db971e2003.webm?t=1767996601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/220c317a7822216c95f229db971e2003.mp4?t=1767996601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择阶段顺序</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，你可以自由选择从飞船上的哪个位置开始！每个阶段都有自己独特的视觉效果、陷阱和敌人。选择最适合你的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/66c46d1fe2ccc911ef8912f0e4347dab.poster.avif?t=1767996601\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/66c46d1fe2ccc911ef8912f0e4347dab.webm?t=1767996601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/66c46d1fe2ccc911ef8912f0e4347dab.mp4?t=1767996601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >获取老大的武器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个关卡的最后，你都将面对游戏中的一个 Boss。打败他们并获得他们的武器，这将使许多挑战变得更加容易。小贴士：每个 BOSS 都有一个弱点，可以让战斗变得更轻松！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/360c04b855eee47cc3deeff8882b9f63.poster.avif?t=1767996601\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/360c04b855eee47cc3deeff8882b9f63.webm?t=1767996601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/360c04b855eee47cc3deeff8882b9f63.mp4?t=1767996601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩得舒心</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RoboGAL 的设计是为了满足那些寻求挑战的玩家，但也为那些正在学习的玩家留出了空间。我们为希望获得更休闲体验的玩家和 2D 游戏资深玩家设计了恰到好处的挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/e16c5a8025f2dd70c235f5cbfab27ecb.avif?t=1767996601\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras_big/e16c5a8025f2dd70c235f5cbfab27ecb.avif?t=1767996601 width=800 height=488 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1767996601\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1767996601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3257150/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1767996601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
